{"title":"车间火花","authors":["聂鑫森"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":7,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间火花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聂鑫森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进 刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我在钢铁的土壤上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁出一刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个螺钉，或是一根轴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活哟，就多了一捧笑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，我才愿意在汗雨和热风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断地进刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把偌大个世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搂在胸前细刻精雕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇 铸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用钢水浇灌火的花朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火花谢后，便结满钢的硕果！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}